NOTICE — third-party content in raw/

The `raw/pdf/` and `raw/html/` directories contain unmodified copies of clinical
forms, screening instruments, and intake packets harvested from publicly
accessible URLs on the websites of academic medical centers, government
agencies, professional societies, and the original instrument authors.

These third-party materials remain the property of their respective copyright
holders. Each FHIR Questionnaire's `copyright` field documents the source
instrument's copyright, and each `meta.source` field links to the original
public URL where the source was retrieved. The harvest is provided here under
fair-use educational and research purposes; if you reuse any individual
instrument, consult the copyright holder's terms (PHQ-9 / GAD-7 / AUDIT-C are
free to use; KOOS / WOMAC / DASH-family / FIQR / ESS / others may require
attribution or a license for commercial use).
